792
00:45:49.664 --> 00:45:50.957
But look on the bright side...

793
00:45:51.791 --> 00:45:53.167
you don't have to follow me anymore.

794
00:45:55.670 --> 00:45:58.422
[Hannah] <i>No one knows what's really</i>
<i>going on in another person's life.

795
00:45:59.715 --> 00:46:02.885
<i>And you never know how what you do</i>
<i>will affect someone else.

796
00:46:03.010 --> 00:46:04.303
Hey. Bryce. what's up?

797
00:46:04.762 --> 00:46:06.097
Hey. Jensen.

798
00:46:07.932 --> 00:46:09.183
<i>And if that goes for me.

799
00:46:09.475 --> 00:46:10.977
<i>it must go for everyone.

800
00:46:13.437 --> 00:46:14.605
<i>Even cheerleaders.

801
00:46:15.481 --> 00:46:16.774
[Clay] Hey. Sheri.

802
00:46:16.941 --> 00:46:18.442
How was the rest of your weekend?

803
00:46:18.859 --> 00:46:19.860
Sorry. what?

804
00:46:19.944 --> 00:46:21.153
You were great at the game.

805
00:46:26.784 --> 00:46:28.536
Jessica. Hey. how are you?

806
00:46:29.870 --> 00:46:30.871
Hey. Clay.

807
00:46:32.498 --> 00:46:34.667
Hey. Justin. good game the other night.

808
00:46:40.923 --> 00:46:42.133
What the fuck is going on?

809
00:46:42.466 --> 00:46:43.634
Who knows anymore?

810
00:46:45.803 --> 00:46:47.179
[P.A. screeches]

811
00:46:47.513 --> 00:46:49.515
[student on P.A.]
<i>Can I have your attention. please?

812
00:46:50.599 --> 00:46:52.518
[Hannah's recording over P.A.]
<i>Hey. it's Hannah.

813
00:46:53.602 --> 00:46:54.812
<i>Hannah Baker.

814
00:46:56.313 --> 00:46:57.690
<i>That's right.

815
00:46:58.024 --> 00:47:01.068
<i>Don't adjust your...</i>
<i>whatever device you're hearing this on.

816
00:47:01.986 --> 00:47:02.820
<i>It's me.

817
00:47:03.738 --> 00:47:05.364
<i>Live and in stereo.

818
00:47:06.949 --> 00:47:08.492
<i>No return engagements.

819
00:47:08.576 --> 00:47:09.702
<i>no encore...

820
00:47:10.244 --> 00:47:13.497
[student over P.A.] ...a<i> huge congrats</i>
<i>to our Tiger team for Saturday's win.

821
00:47:13.581 --> 00:47:15.875
<i>A special shout-out to Zach Dempsey.

822
