00:47:18.502 --> 00:47:19.962
<i>In other athletic news.

824
00:47:20.046 --> 00:47:21.922
<i>the Lady Tigers won their game

825
00:47:22.006 --> 00:47:24.091
<i>by a score of 54-32.

826
00:47:27.303 --> 00:47:28.679
Thought you said this wasn't a test.

827
00:47:29.764 --> 00:47:31.349
'Cause this looks like a test.

828
00:47:31.515 --> 00:47:33.559
It's not. Mr. Pratters. I assure you.

829
