It is a character-building questionnaire
that assesses

830
00:47:36.771 --> 00:47:38.689
personal strengths and weaknesses.

831
00:47:58.250 --> 00:47:59.627
Excuse me. Mrs. Bradley?

832
00:47:59.794 --> 00:48:00.878
Yes. Clay.

833
00:48:01.420 --> 00:48:03.756
How important was it to you
to help Hannah Baker?

834
00:48:06.550 --> 00:48:09.261
Extremely important to me. Clay.
Why do you ask?

835
00:48:11.889 --> 00:48:14.225
Remember that note you got
in your bag last year?

836
00:48:15.893 --> 00:48:17.853
The one about
not feeling anything anymore?

837
00:48:22.274 --> 00:48:23.442
It was from Hannah.

838
00:48:25.611 --> 00:48:27.988
Okay. uh. why do you think that is?

839
00:48:28.072 --> 00:48:29.198
[door opens]

840
00:48:30.407 --> 00:48:31.408
-Mrs. Bradley?
-Yes?

841
