to follow through on a promise.

848
00:48:49.260 --> 00:48:50.302
[Courtney] Don't worry. Clay.

849
00:48:50.636 --> 00:48:52.304
I almost forgot too.

850
00:48:53.389 --> 00:48:54.473
Forgot what?

851
00:48:54.557 --> 00:48:57.309
Courtney and Clay. these are
our new foreign exchange students

852
00:48:57.393 --> 00:48:59.228
joining us this semester.

853
00:48:59.437 --> 00:49:03.732
This is Jhene. Fynn.
Mahla and Deep.

854
00:49:03.899 --> 00:49:06.527
Uh. Courtney and Clay
will be helping you out.

855
00:49:06.610 --> 00:49:09.405
They are on the Honor Board
and they'll be giving you the tour.

856
00:49:09.738 --> 00:49:11.031
The insider's tour!

857
00:49:11.282 --> 00:49:13.701
All the secrets that you need to know.

858
00:49:16.704 --> 00:49:17.997
Okay. great.

859
00:49:21.458 --> 00:49:22.543
[Clay] <i>So as you can see.

860
00:49:22.626 --> 00:49:25.421
it's one of the finest high school
parking lots in the world.

861
00:49:25.921 --> 00:49:27.298
Oh. and right here is the library.

862
00:49:27.381 --> 00:49:31.051
where you can find books and tables
and chairs and all that stuff...

863
00:49:31.468 --> 00:49:32.720
state-of-the-art computers.

864
00:49:32.803 --> 00:49:34.805
at least if the art was ten years ago...

865
00:49:35.139 --> 00:49:36.265
and friendly librarians.

866
00:49:36.432 --> 00:49:39.268
Not super bright always. but friendly.

867
00:49:42.771 --> 00:49:44.315
Oh. wait. everyone.

868
00:49:44.565 --> 00:49:47.234
It's Justin Foley and Zach Dempsey.

869
00:49:47.318 --> 00:49:49.278
star basketball players
here at Liberty High.

870
00:49:49.361 --> 00:49:51.697
Hey. Justin. where's my bike?

871
00:49:52.114 --> 00:49:53.240
Justin stole my bike.

872
00:49:53.824 --> 00:49:55.284
What the fuck?
What are you doing?

873
00:49:55.367 --> 00:49:57.369
I'm giving our new
foreign exchange students a tour.

874
00:49:57.453 --> 00:49:59.830
Figured they should know
who owns the school. right. you guys?

875
00:49:59.914 --> 00:50:00.915
Clay.

876
00:50:01.040 --> 00:50:02.333
Right. right. Moving on.

877
00:50:02.458 --> 00:50:03.459
Where were we?

878
00:50:03.542 --> 00:50:04.543
Right. The auditorium.

879
00:50:04.627 --> 00:50:06.212
Oh. oh. but before we go...

880
00:50:07.004 --> 00:50:08.923
I want to show you something super cool.

881
00:50:09.465 --> 00:50:11.342
-Okay?
-Clay. cut it out.

882
00:50:12.051 --> 00:50:13.594
Look at these lockers.

883
00:50:14.178 --> 00:50:15.721
They all look alike. right?

884
00:50:17.765 --> 00:50:18.599
Not this one.

885
00:50:21.060 --> 00:50:22.228
This one is special.

886
00:50:23.145 --> 00:50:25.064
It belonged to a girl who killed herself.

887
00:50:25.272 --> 00:50:26.482
Clay. come on.

888
00:50:26.565 --> 00:50:29.485
You see all these "don't kill yourself"
posters up on the wall?

889
00:50:29.610 --> 00:50:30.861
They weren't up before.

890
00:50:30.945 --> 00:50:33.280
They put them up
<i>because </i>she killed herself.

891
00:50:33.405 --> 00:50:34.406
And why did she do it?

892
00:50:34.490 --> 00:50:36.283
Because the kids here
treated her like shit!

893
00:50:36.367 --> 00:50:37.618
[Justin] Jensen. that's enough.

894
00:50:37.743 --> 00:50:39.787
But no one wants to admit it.
so they paint over the bathrooms

895
00:50:39.870 --> 00:50:42.706
and put up a memorial. because that's
the kind of school that this is.

896
00:50:42.790 --> 00:50:45.417
Everyone is just so <i>nice</i>
until they drive you to kill yourself.

897
00:50:45.626 --> 00:50:47.586
And sooner or later.
the truth will come out.

898
00:50:49.630 --> 00:50:50.714
It's gonna come out.

899
00:50:55.302 --> 00:50:57.721
Right. Tony? Right? You know the truth.

900
00:50:58.138 --> 00:50:59.098
[Mr. Porter] Clay.

901
00:51:00.849 --> 00:51:02.851
I think you should come with me right now.

902
00:51:04.186 --> 00:51:05.980
Get to class. everybody!

903
00:51:06.563 --> 00:51:08.148
All you. get to class.

904
00:51:11.443 --> 00:51:12.653
Welcome to Liberty High.

905
00:51:13.654 --> 00:51:14.655
Let's go.

906
00:51:24.456 --> 00:51:25.457
Okay.

